  "stac_version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "This dataset provides daily ungridded (L2B) SIF and surface reflectance estimates derived from TROPOMI observations covering the period May 2018-March 2021. SIF data are estimated from two fitting windows: from the 743-758 nm window (baseline product) and from the extended 735-758 nm window (secondary product). The L2B TROPOSIF products are provided in netCDF-4 files.",
